name: Indian Ridge Florida
overview:
Florida villa holiday home rental

Indian Ridge Our Florida villa on Indian Ridge is a spacious villa well designed with the benefit of a caring home owners association that cares for the community making Indian Ridge villas a safe clean place to live and holiday.

The mornings are quite except for the children having fun in the pool at holiday villas.

When we holiday in Florida we like having one full day at a park and one day off by the pool and maybe go out for some shopping late afternoon.

Indian ridge villas have three play areas on the development, which the children are welcome to use. We also have community tennis courts and basketball ring for your pleasure.

The community pool is also available but I guess having your own private pool will mean you donâ€™t want to use the community pool.

Orlando villas are the best way to holiday in Florida why stay in a small hotel room when you can enjoy the benefits of Florida villas.
